reviewText:
Great game!

Finished in 7 hours on hard.

+ Immersion;
+ Various weapons to use (melee and ranged);
+ Great story;
+ Great crime scene feature with riddles/puzzles;
+ Challenging gameplay.

- Out dated graphics and mechanics;
- Repetitive enemy models;
- Important buttons unassigned;
- Bugs: low.
- Poor setting options.

Final score: 8/10
